ome》</a>并表演 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/usher-to-headline-2024-super-bowl-half-time-show-3503289">超级碗中场秀</a>。单曲“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/usher-new-single-glu-after-a-three-year-hiatus-new-album-3415529">GLU</a> ”、“Good Good”（来自<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/summer-walker">Summer Walker</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/21-savage">21 Savage</a> ）和“Boyfriend”预计都会出现在专辑中。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="USHER - 男朋友（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/56CW4SIqBzk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>与此同时，Doja Cat 于九月发行了她的最新专辑《Scarlet》。<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/doja-cat-scarlet-review-lyrics-tracklist-3501824">在我们的三星级评论中</a>，我们说《Scarlet》“构成了一张过长、有点重复但最终引人注目的两半专辑……不过，到了这个阶段，毫无疑问多贾已经表达了她的观点——她没有”除了做她自己之外，我不欠我们任何东西。”</p><p> Usher 和 Doja Cat 也将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-doja-cat-royal-blood-and-more-lead-line-up-for-bbc-radio-1-live-lounge-month-3493501">在 BBC Live Lounge 表演</a>。到目前为止，该系列已由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/troye-sivan">特洛伊·西万</a>等人主演。</p><p> 《 <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-usher-serenade-doja-cat-at-his-las-vegas-residency-3519045">观看亚瑟小夜曲 Doja Cat》在拉斯维加斯驻场演出的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
